import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  import { Playground, PropsTable } from 'docz';
import Input from './Input';

export default ({components, ...props}) => <MDXTag name="wrapper"  components={components}>
<MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"input"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h1" props={{"aria-hidden":true,"href":"#input"}}><MDXTag name="span" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"className":"icon-link"}}>{`#`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>{`Input`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`문자열을 입력받는 컴포넌트입니다.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"props"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h2" props={{"aria-hidden":true,"href":"#props"}}><MDXTag name="span" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"className":"icon-link"}}>{`#`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>{`Props`}</MDXTag>
<PropsTable of={Input} />
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"basic-usage"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h2" props={{"aria-hidden":true,"href":"#basic-usage"}}><MDXTag name="span" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"className":"icon-link"}}>{`#`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>{`Basic usage`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={1} __code={`<Input placeholder="입력해주세요." />`} __scope={{props,Input}}>
  <Input placeholder="입력해주세요." />
</Playground>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"inline-inputs"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h2" props={{"aria-hidden":true,"href":"#inline-inputs"}}><MDXTag name="span" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"className":"icon-link"}}>{`#`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>{`Inline inputs`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={2} __code={`<Input inline placeholder="입력해주세요." />
<Input inline placeholder="입력해주세요." />`} __scope={{props,Input}}>
  <Input
    inline
    placeholder="입력해주세요."
  />
  <Input
    inline
    placeholder="입력해주세요."
  />
</Playground>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"with-allow-message"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h2" props={{"aria-hidden":true,"href":"#with-allow-message"}}><MDXTag name="span" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"className":"icon-link"}}>{`#`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>{`With allow message`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={3} __code={`<Input allowMessage="올바른 값입니다." />`} __scope={{props,Input}}>
  <Input allowMessage="올바른 값입니다." />
</Playground>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"with-error-message"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h2" props={{"aria-hidden":true,"href":"#with-error-message"}}><MDXTag name="span" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"className":"icon-link"}}>{`#`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>{`With error message`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={4} __code={`<Input errorMessage="특수문자를 제외하고 입력해주세요." />`} __scope={{props,Input}}>
  <Input errorMessage="특수문자를 제외하고 입력해주세요." />
</Playground>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"with-warn-message"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h2" props={{"aria-hidden":true,"href":"#with-warn-message"}}><MDXTag name="span" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"className":"icon-link"}}>{`#`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>{`With warn message`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={5} __code={`<Input warnMessage="보안에 취약한 값입니다." />`} __scope={{props,Input}}>
  <Input warnMessage="보안에 취약한 값입니다." />
</Playground>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"disabled-input"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h2" props={{"aria-hidden":true,"href":"#disabled-input"}}><MDXTag name="span" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"className":"icon-link"}}>{`#`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>{`Disabled Input`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={6} __code={`<Input placeholder="잠금 상태입니다." disabled />`} __scope={{props,Input}}>
  <Input placeholder="잠금 상태입니다." disabled />
</Playground></MDXTag>
